title: Going For It & All Those Blocks We Put In Our Way
description:
Leap and the net will appear.  Jillian knows...she tested it.  Then Jillian gets right into calls dealing with questions on fitness, nutrition, inspiration and overall wellness.  She speaks with two very cool women who are dealing with mental blocks and the oh so gradual impending menopause.
